raw.subject: The Getting Started Guide is a non-confidential document that gives an overview of Arm Corstone-500. The guide describes the IP in Arm Corstone SSE-500 Example Subsystem, the prototyping and modelling options, and programming information for the subsystem. Read this guide if you are new to Arm IP or want an overview of how Corstone-500 can be used as the starting point for creating your own Internet of Things (IoT) application.
